<!channel> Today is our last official day here on Water Ave! :partyparrot: (and dennis’ last day with us :cry:) A few reminders:

-your desk must be packed by 5:30pm today!
-we will be packing up the rest of the office late this afternoon, including office supplies and kitchen items. Please return all dishes to the kitchen before you leave today.

also! if you have stuff in one of the lockers in social, please don’t forget to pack that up as well :slightly_smiling_face:
